            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hello everyone. My daughter has been going to Kangaroo Kids school since last 1.5 years   We are happy to share our HAPPY HAPPY experinces with the school.\n\nWe had put her into this school very early at age 2 years. Since she was very little at time, we were a bit worried about how she will cope up. But we were very happy to see that she was taken very good care in the school. There were no problems in getting her adjusted in the class.\n\nWe are also very happy to see how she has shaped up as a child and has learned so many things in school so early on. It helped us in many ways.\n\nThe whole atmosphere of the school is very\npositive and welcoming.  Feels good everytime we are in the school. All teachers and staff are very warm in their approach ,\n\nI would say keep up the good work. Overall a wonderful experience. Thank you for all your help and support extended to all parents like us.",
          "publisher": {
